<div class="jumbotron container bg-white text-center border-bottom rounded-0 pb-5">
  <h1 class="display-4" style="font-weight: 200;">Contact Us</h1>
  <p class="lead text-muted mt-2">Ask us anything! It's what defines us.</p>
</div>

<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-4">
      <ul class="list-group mb-4">
        <li class="list-group-item list-group-item-action active"><h1 style="font-weight: 300;">Need support?</h1></li>
        <li class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">🛠️ Our support team is here for you. Describe your frustration and we will fix it right away!</li>
        <li class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">✓ Need help with you Account? Let's solve that together!</li>
      </ul>

      <ul class="list-group mb-5">
        <li class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">🙋 Wanna help us out? Coding, Designing, Mentoring and lots more options! More help means we can deliver updates faster.</li>
        <li class="list-group-item list-group-item-action active text-light"><h1 style="font-weight: 300;">Feedback</h1></li>
        <li class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">🐞 Did you just discover a bug? (Fantastic! You made our job easier 😉)</li>
        <li class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">💡 Do you have a suggestion? A recommendation? (We 💕those)</li>
        <li class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">👍 Just give us a thumbs up! Our hard working engineers will really appreciate! 🤙</li>
        <li class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">🔔 Looking for some tips and tricks? We will hit you up with those ASAP!</li>
      </ul>

    </div>

    <div class="col-sm-8 mb-5" id="formCol">
      <form id="feedbackForm" enctype="multipart/form-data">
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="name">Name</label>
          <input type="text" class="form-control" id="name" placeholder="Your name">
          <small id="emailHelp" class="form-text text-muted">We'll never share your name with anyone else.</small>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="email">Email address</label>
          <input type="email" class="form-control" id="email" aria-describedby="emailHelp" placeholder="Enter email">
          <small id="emailHelp" class="form-text text-muted">We'll never share your email with anyone else.</small>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="subject">Subject</label>
          <input autocomplete="off" type="text" class="form-control" id="subject" placeholder="Subject">
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="editor">Please describe your experience</label>
          <!-- <textarea class="form-control" id="exampleFormControlTextarea1" name="description" rows="3"></textarea> -->

          <div id="editor">

          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="fileUpload">File Upload (optional)</label>
          <input name="file" type="file" class="form-control-file" id="fileUpload" multiple="">
        </div>

        <div class="form-group form-check">
          <input type="checkbox" class="form-check-input" id="agreementCheck">
          <label class="form-check-label" for="agreementCheck">I verify that I am not trying to <em>spam</em> and would like to receive appropriate consideration to my message</label>
        </div>
        <button type="submit" id="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Submit</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

<script type="text/javascript" src="/js/contact-quill-post.js"></script>
